app.comment:
Displays your current speed and heading in real-time.

Features:
- Settings menu allows you to customize portions of the UI and functionality
- Toggle night mode from home screen
- Customize the background with a solid color, image from the phone's library, or the the phone's camera
- Optional speech functionality utilizes offline caching to reduce delay normally caused by the need to be online for word translation
- Configurable speed thresholds can be configured to alert you when you reach certain speeds
- Rotate phone left to view both your current and all-time average speed, top speed, and distance traveled
- When the tile is pinned the back displays your all-time average speed, top speed, and distance traveled

*All-time average speed is calculated upon script startup
